Package Model

Class ReplenishmentRequest

java.lang.Object
Model.ReplenishmentRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ReplenishmentRequest extends Object implements Serializable
The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish stock levels for a specific medicine.

This class includes details such as the request ID, associated medicine ID, requested stock level, and the status of the request. It is serializable, allowing it to be saved and retrieved from persistent storage.

Key Features:

  • Tracks the unique request ID.
  • Maintains the ID of the medicine for which the request is made.
  • Records the requested stock level.
  • Stores the current status of the request using InventoryRequestStatus.
